An hour later he spoke to a friend: 'I’ll get back to you on that. I’m on top of a really high mountain in Mexico and I’m not exactly sure how to get down.' 

Khalsa was only carrying a liter of water and trail mix when he left and was wearing a T-shirt and shorts.

