Before news of his death, she told CBS2: 'We've done everything within our power, and we are so confused about the process, and confused about why T-Mobile will not release this information.

T-Mobile told the station: 'By law, we can only work directly with law enforcement, and privacy laws prohibit us from discussing any specific actions we take. 

'We can confirm we received contact with the FBI and are working with them.'

